{"tid":1434543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人地要唔要出黎到底關你叉事？","createTime":"2019-08-08T21:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T00:46:44.000Z","uid":290683,"like":28,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c64ee367ae775b962ad687258cb791628106689","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:00:12.000Z","msg":"唔出黎就俾你地話冇出力<br />\n<br />\n咁人地唔可以有唔講得嘅原因？<br />\n人地唔可以細膽唔敢出棃？<br />\n人地唔可以身體唔允許出唔到棃？<br />\n人地唔可以俾父母禁門？<br />\n<br />\n唔通選擇留響屋企忙住做文宣、發post、轉post、prin野、籌錢幫你地買物資、做鍵盤戰士去影響一啲唔係同溫層嘅人等等等等就唔叫出力？<br />\n你嗰套先為之出力？<br />\n<br />\n成日話你啲FD冇一次有去一味揾藉口點點點，話唔定人地只係響度制造不在場證據呢，一定要話俾你聽有去㗎？佢想自己去唔得㗎咩？<br />\n<br />\n已經連續兩日睇到兩個類似嘅post，開始睇到嬲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係做你嗰套就唔鐘意<br />\n唔鐘意都算，仲想管人地<br />\n你家陣住海邊啊？<br />\n你咁樣仲學乜人講自由？<br />\n你咁樣同共產黨嗰啲獨裁撚有乜份別？<br />\n硬係要道德綁架下人地先舒服<br />\n咩叫各自各爬山啊<br />\n就係叫你唔好理人想點做啊！<br />\n係都要覺得出棃先叫有付出<br />\n咁你不如直接叫人去衝好過啦？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人地同我地企喺同一陣線咪算囉，管咁多做乜啫？你再搞得兩搞，搞到人地走撚左去支持對家到時你就知味道！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有啊！<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>你地班友仔遇到對家嘅人嘅時候同我冷靜啲！</strong></span><br />\n除非佢地突然走埋黎喐手打你再還手<br />\n唔係嘅話，唔該！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔！好！主！動！去！撩！事！鬥！非！</span></span><br />\n你地嘅言行舉止會影響到對家對我地嘅印象同形象，唔要求你地做紳士淑女，但起碼都<strong>禮貌啲</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地係要增加同伴<br />\n將佢地主動轉軚過黎我地呢邊<br />\n而唔係增加佢地對我地嘅仇恨<br />\n我知大家都好撚憎對家，我都一撚樣<br />\n但唔該控制一下自己嘅情緒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好一見到唔係自己同溫層就衝鳩埋去係咁屌<br />\n咁樣人地只會對我地越黎越反感<br />\n咁唔係好事"},{"pid":"ab6ea211855a96a7838b679fc43ddb88df7c96f9","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f40dc90d44138672b864d713be82d32ad31ef63","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ad0d54657298d1a875e0ec603104af1c975774","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b3696e943ffaa2feca087bfbda203bc4dc807a","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151cd66824b068ac53eae7e1fc39ad2e911663cc","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa16b80dc8c7c675be8f9ea490eb060e134c1b2","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7256a8b2edb81225a5041f1dc86058cf219e8e90","tid":1434543,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:07:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a56d18fd80f391eea12d7d0a391c64ebd9458e02","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035a3ea212c528d6a6ab63f5a147da3a2cf0e171","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23543677fa3a2aeadfefd9dae4fea456186f12b","tid":1434543,"uid":290683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbe3c2f2e1b0c0024d34a0ffecfba2f600f7d4a"